    <briefdescription>
<para>AGC state. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Allocate with <ref refid="agc__core_8h_1a513369f303365f4d356d9eb7ae80cf3b" kindref="member">agc_create()</ref>. <computeroutput>ref_db</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>loop_bw</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>alpha</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>decim</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>clip_db</computeroutput> are configuration (readable and writable at runtime); <computeroutput>gain_db</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>p_avg</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>g_last</computeroutput> are the loop&apos;s internal memory. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
